#. Tag: title
#: usermenu.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "User-Configurable Menu"
msgstr "Meni, ki ga lahko konfigurira uporabnik"

#. Tag: title
#: usermenu.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:7
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kile; supports a user-configurable menu, which will appear as a part of "
"&kile;'s menu. This menu can be configured using &kile;'s configuration "
"dialog with <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure "
"Kile</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>User Menu</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"&kile; podpira uporabniško nastavljiv meni, ki bo prikazan kot del  menija "
"&kile;. Ta meni lahko nastavite s konfiguracijo &kile;  dialog "
"z<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj Kile</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Uporabniški meni</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Configure the user menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Konfiguriraj uporabniški meni</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Configure the user menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfiguriraj uporabniški meni</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "You have two options where to place this menu:"
msgstr "Na voljo imate dve možnosti, kam postaviti ta meni:"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"either the menu <guimenu>User Menu</guimenu> will appear in the main menu "
"bar between the menus <guimenu>LaTeX</guimenu> and <guimenu>Wizard</guimenu> "
"and the configuration wizard <guimenuitem>Edit User Menu</guimenuitem> in "
"the <guimenu>Wizard</guimenu> menu"
msgstr ""
"bodisi da se <guimenu>Uporabniški meni</guimenu> prikaže v glavni menijski "
"vrstici  med meniji <guimenu>LaTeX</guimenu> in <guimenu>Čarovnik</guimenu> "
"inbodisi v čarovniku za konfiguracijo <guimenuitem>Urejanje uporabniškega "
"menija</guimenuitem> v meniju <guimenu>Čarovnik</guimenu>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>User Menu is placed in the main menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Uporabniški meni je postavljen v glavni meni</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>User Menu is placed in the main menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Uporabniški meni je postavljen v glavni meni</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"or both items will appear at the bottom of the <guimenu>LaTeX</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"ali pa se bosta oba elementa pojavila na dnu menija <guimenu>LaTeX</guimenu>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>User Menu as a part of the LaTeX menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Uporabniški meni kot del menija LaTeX</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>User Menu as a part of the LaTeX menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Uporabniški meni kot del menija LaTeX</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Already existing user-defined tags from older versions of &kile; are "
"automatically transformed into the new user-configurable menu. The tags are "
"saved in a file called <filename>usertags.xml</filename> and like all menu "
"definition files, they can be found in the local user menu directory of "
"&kile;: <filename>KILE_APP_DIR/usermenu/</filename>, &eg; <filename>/home/"
"user/.kde/share/apps/kile/usermenu/</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Že obstoječe uporabniško definirane oznake iz starejših različic &kile; "
"samodejno preoblikuje v nov uporabniško nastavljiv meni. Oznake so shranjene "
"v datoteko, imenovano <filename>usertags.xml</filename> in kot vse datoteke "
"z definicijami menijev tudi to najdete v imeniku lokalnega uporabniškega "
"menija &kile;: <filename>KILE_APP_DIR/usermenu/</filename>, &eg; <filename>/"
"home/user/.kde/share/apps/kile/usermenu/</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use different menu definition files for different tasks. Call the "
"user menu wizard <menuchoice><guimenu>Wizard</guimenu><guisubmenu>Edit User "
"Menu</guisubmenu></menuchoice> or <menuchoice><guimenu>LaTeX</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Edit User Menu</guisubmenu></menuchoice> to install or "
"edit a menu definition file."
msgstr ""
"Za različna opravila lahko uporabite različne datoteke z definicijami "
"menija. Pokličite čarovnika za uporabniški meni "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Čarovnik</guimenu><guisubmenu>Uredi uporabniški meni</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> ali <menuchoice><guimenu>LaTeX</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Uredi uporabniški meni</guisubmenu></menuchoice> za "
"namestitev ali urejanje datoteke z definicijo menija."

#. Tag: title
#: usermenu.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wizard"
msgstr "Čarovnik"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can create new or change existing menus with a comfortable user menu "
"configuration wizard found at <menuchoice><guimenu>Wizard</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Edit User Menu</guisubmenu></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Z udobnim uporabniškim menijem lahko ustvarite nove ali spremenite obstoječe "
"menije čarovnika za konfiguracijo najdete v <menuchoice><guimenu>Čarovnik</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Uredi uporabniški meni</guisubmenu></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>User Menu Wizard</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Čarovnik za uporabniški meni</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>User Menu Wizard</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Čarovnik za uporabniški meni</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the left side you will see an existing menu-tree. Like a standard menu, "
"three different kinds of menu items are available:"
msgstr ""
"Na levi strani boste videli obstoječe drevo menijev. Kot standardni meni so "
"na voljo tri različne vrste elementov menija:"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "standard menu entries, which are assigned to an action"
msgstr "standardni menijski vnosi, ki so dodeljeni dejanju"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "submenus, which contain more menu items"
msgstr "podmeniji, ki vsebujejo več elementov menija"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "separators, to get a visible structure of all entries."
msgstr "ločilniki, da dobite vidno strukturo vseh vnosov."

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To modify this menu, use the six buttons on the left side. More possible "
"actions are available in the context menu of already existing menu items."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti ta meni, uporabite šest gumbov na levi strani. Več "
"možnih dejanj je na voljo v kontekstnem meniju že obstoječih elementov "
"menija."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>User-Defined Menutree</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Uporabniško definirano drevo menijev</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>User-Defined Menutree</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Uporabniško definirano drevo menijev</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each standard menu item is assigned to one of three action types, where each "
"of them has different attributes, which could be set:"
msgstr ""
"Vsaka standardna menijska postavka je dodeljena eni od treh vrst dejanj, "
"kjer ima vsaka od njih različne atribute, ki jih je mogoče nastaviti:"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Text:</guilabel>&nbsp; &kile; gives you the ability to make your "
"own tags. A tag is similar to a shortcut that launches some command or "
"writes frequently-used texts, &eg; Joe Sixpack often uses the sentences "
"<userinput>Hi, I have been inserted ...</userinput>. This tag will be "
"inserted at the current cursor position, when this action is called (see "
"above). Metachars are also available (see <xref linkend="
"\"id_usermenu_placeholders\" role=\"select: title pageabbrv\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Besedilo:</guilabel>&nbsp; &kile; vam daje možnost, da naredite "
"svoje lastne oznake. Oznaka je podobna bližnjici, ki zažene nek ukaz oz. "
"piše pogosto uporabljenobesedilo, npr. Joe Sixpack pogosto uporablja stavke "
"<userinput>Živjo, bil sem  vstavljen...</userinput>. Ta oznaka bo vstavljena "
"na trenutni položaj kazalca, ko je to dejanje klicano (glejte zgoraj). Na "
"voljo so tudi metaznaki (glejte <xref  linkend=\"id_usermenu_placeholders\" "
"role=\"select: title pageabbrv\"/>)."

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Insert file contents:</guilabel>&nbsp; Inserts the complete "
"contents of a given file."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Vstavi vsebino datoteke:</guilabel>&nbsp; Vstavi celotno vsebino "
"dane datoteke."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Insert file contents</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Vstavi vsebino datoteke</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Insert file contents</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Vstavi vsebino datoteke</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Execute an external program:</guilabel>&nbsp; The output of this "
"program can be inserted into the opened document. Metachar <userinput>%M</"
"userinput> is also possible in the command line of this program, as the "
"selected text will be saved in a temporary file. Use <userinput>%M</"
"userinput> for the filename of this temporary file."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Izvedi zunanji program:</guilabel>&nbsp; Rezultat tega programa "
"lahko vstavite v odprt dokument. Metaznak <userinput>%M</userinput> je tudi "
"mogoč v ukazni vrstici tega programa, kot bo izbrano besedilo shranjeno v "
"začasni datoteki. Za ime te začasne datoteke uporabite <userinput>%M</"
"userinput>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Execute an external program</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Izvedi zunanji program</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Execute an external program</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izvedi zunanji program</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If some important information for an action is missing, menu items are "
"colored red. This may be a nonexisting file"
msgstr ""
"Če nekatere pomembne informacije za dejanje manjkajo, se menijski elementi "
"obarvajo rdeče. To je lahko neobstoječa datoteka"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Nonexisting file</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Neobstoječa datoteka</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Nonexisting file</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Neobstoječa datoteka</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"or a missing title for the menu entry, which will be shown with question "
"marks as <userinput>???</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"ali manjkajoči naslov za menijski vnos, ki bo prikazan z vprašaji kot "
"<userinput>???</userinput>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Missing title of a menu entry</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Manjka naslov menijskega vnosa</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Missing title of a menu entry</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Manjka naslov vnosa v meniju</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you open the context menu of such a red colored menu item, you will get "
"an additional option for more information concerning this error."
msgstr ""
"Če odprete kontekstni meni take rdeče obarvane postavke menija, boste "
"prejeli dodatno možnost za več informacij o tej napaki."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Additional info</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Dodatne informacije</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Additional info</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Dodatne informacije</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More information may also be available using the <guilabel>What's this</"
"guilabel> feature of most widgets."
msgstr ""
"Več informacij je lahko na voljo tudi s funkcijo <guilabel>Kaj je to</"
"guilabel> večine gradnikov."

#. Tag: title
#: usermenu.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Placeholders"
msgstr "Oznake mesta"

#. Tag: title
#: usermenu.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert Text"
msgstr "Vstavi besedilo"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are some placeholders you can use in your user-defined tags: "
"<userinput>%C</userinput>, <userinput>%B</userinput>, <userinput>%M</"
"userinput>, <userinput>%E</userinput>, <userinput>%R</userinput> and "
"<userinput>%T</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja nekaj oznak mest, ki jih lahko uporabite v svojih uporabniško "
"določenih oznakah: <userinput>%C</userinput>, <userinput>%B</userinput>, "
"<userinput>%M</userinput>, <userinput>%E</userinput>, <userinput>%R</"
"userinput> in <userinput>%T</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>%C</userinput>:&nbsp; this is where the cursor will be placed "
"after the insertion of a user-defined tag."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>%C</userinput>:&nbsp; tukaj bo postavljen kazalec po vstavitvi "
"uporabniško določene oznake."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Cursor Position (%C)</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Položaj kazalca (%C)</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Cursor Position (%C)</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Položaj kazalca (%C)</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>%B</userinput>:&nbsp; will be replaced by a bullet (see <xref "
"linkend=\"editing_bullets\" role=\"select: title pageabbrv\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>%B</userinput>:&nbsp; bo nadomeščena s točko naštevanja (glejte "
"<xref  linkend=\"editing_bullets\" role=\"select: title pageabbrv\"/>)."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Bullet (%B)</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Točka naštevanja (%B)</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Bullet (%B)</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Točka naštevanja (%B)</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>%M</userinput>:&nbsp; will be replaced by the selected text."
msgstr "<userinput>%M</userinput>:&nbsp; bo nadomestilo izbrano besedilo."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Selected Text (%M)</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Izbrano besedilo (%M)</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Selected Text (%M)</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izbrano besedilo (%M)</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>%E</userinput>:&nbsp; denotes the indentation depth of text "
"inside an environment."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>%E</userinput>:&nbsp; označuje globino zamika besedila znotraj "
"okolja."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Indentation of environment text (%E)</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Zamik okolja besedila (%E)</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Indentation of environment text (%E)</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Zamik okolja besedila (%E)</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>%R</userinput>:&nbsp; will call a reference-dialog to choose a "
"label which has already been defined. This can be used to refer to a "
"predefined label, which you can choose from a drop-down list (see also "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>LaTeX</guimenu><guimenuitem>References</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>ref</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>LaTeX</guimenu><guimenuitem>References</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>pageref</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>%R</userinput>:&nbsp; bo poklical referenčno pogovorno okno za "
"izbiro   oznake, ki je že definirana. To se lahko uporablja za sklicevanje "
"na vnaprej določeno oznako, ki jo lahko izbirate s spustnega seznama (glejte "
"tudi <menuchoice><guimenu>LaTeX</guimenu><guimenuitem>Reference</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>ref</guimenuitem></menuchoice> oz."
"<menuchoice><guimenu>LaTeX</guimenu><guimenuitem>Reference</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>pageref</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>References (%R)</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Reference (%R)</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>References (%R)</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Reference (%R)</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>%T</userinput>:&nbsp; will call a citation-dialog to choose an "
"already defined citation. The same as using <menuchoice><guimenu>LaTeX</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>References</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>cite</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> a list with all the citation keys pops up."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>%T</userinput>:&nbsp; bo poklical pogovorno okno za navajanje, da "
"izbere že definiran citat. Enako kot pri uporabi <menuchoice><guimenu>LaTeX</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Reference</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>cit</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> se pojavi seznam z vsemi ključi za navedbe."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Citation Keys (%T)</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Ključi navedb (%T)</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Citation Keys (%T)</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Ključi navedb (%T)</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let's consider another example, with the following macro <userinput>"
"\\frac{%M}{%C}</userinput>. First, we select a number in our text, let's say "
"<userinput>42</userinput>. Now we invoke this macro and obtain <userinput>"
"\\frac{42}{}</userinput> with the cursor located within the second pair of "
"brackets."
msgstr ""
"Oglejmo si še en primer z naslednjim makrom <userinput>\\frac{%M}{%C}</"
"userinput>. Najprej izberemo številko v svojem besedilu, recimo "
"<userinput>42</userinput>. Zdaj pokličemo ta makro in pridobimo <userinput>"
"\\frac{42}{}</userinput> s kazalcem v drugem paru oklepajev."

#. Tag: title
#: usermenu.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert File Contents"
msgstr "Vstavi vsebino datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to insert the contents of a text file, you could use the same "
"placeholders."
msgstr ""
"Če želite vstaviti vsebino besedilne datoteke, lahko uporabite iste oznake "
"mest."

#. Tag: title
#: usermenu.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Execute A Program"
msgstr "Izvedi program"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to execute an external program, only the <userinput>%M</"
"userinput> for selected text is recognized in the command line. The "
"selection will be saved in a temporary file and the placeholder <userinput>"
"%M</userinput> is replaced with this filename."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izvesti zunanji program, je za izbrano besedilo prepoznan samo "
"<userinput>%M</userinput> v ukazni vrstici. Izbor bo shranjen v začasno "
"datoteko in nadomestni znak <userinput>%M</userinput> je nadomeščen s tem "
"imenom datoteke."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Execute an external program (%M)</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Izvedi zunanji program (%M)</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Execute an external program (%M)</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izvedi zunanji program (%M)</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another placeholder is <userinput>%S</userinput>, which is replaced by the "
"complete base name of the current document without the path. This base name "
"consists of all characters in the file up to (but not including) the last "
"'.' character."
msgstr ""
"Druga nadomestni znak je <userinput>%S</userinput>, ki je nadomeščen s "
"celotnim osnovnim imenom trenutnega dokumenta brez poti. To osnovno ime "
"sestoji iz vsehznakov v datoteki do (vendar brez) zadnje pike '.'."

#. Tag: title
#: usermenu.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameter"
msgstr "Parameter"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most menu entries may have additional self-explaining parameters, which may "
"be checked. If some of these parameters are not available for some kind of "
"action, they are disabled."
msgstr ""
"Večina menijskih vnosov ima lahko dodatne samorazlagajoče parametre, ki jih "
"je lahko preveriti. Če nekateri od teh parametrov niso na voljo za neko "
"vrsto dejanja, soonemogočeni."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>User Menu Parameter</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Parameter uporabniškega menija</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:344
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>User Menu Parameter</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Parameter uporabniškega menija</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:349
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here is one example for executing an external program:"
msgstr "Tukaj je en primer za izvajanje zunanjega programa:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Parameter example</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Primer parametra</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Parameter example</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Primer parametra</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can see that a <userinput>perl</userinput> script is called, which "
"should work with current selection. The <guilabel>Needs selected text</"
"guilabel> parameter is checked to assure a selection. The output of this "
"script will be inserted (<guilabel>Insert the output of the chosen program</"
"guilabel>) and replace the current selection (<guilabel>Replace selected "
"text</guilabel>), but not selected itself."
msgstr ""
"Vidite lahko, da je poklican skript <userinput>perl</userinput>, kar bi "
"moralo delovati s trenutno izbiro. Parameter <guilabel>Potrebuje izbrano "
"besedilo</guilabel> je preverjen, da zagotovite izbiro. Izhod tega skripta "
"bo vstavljen (<guilabel>Vstavi izhod izbranega programa</guilabel>) in "
"zamenjaj trenutni izbor (<guilabel>Zamenjaj izbrano besedilo</guilabel>), "
"vendar ni sam izbran."

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Of course you can also call your own programs or scripts. For example select "
"a list of numbers, separated by spaces, and call a script or Perl program, "
"which transforms this selection into &latex; code for a matrix. Whatever "
"your ideas may be, you can realize them using the following usermenu entry."
msgstr ""
"Seveda lahko pokličete tudi svoje programe ali skripte. Na primer izberite "
"seznam številk, ločenih s presledki, in pokličite skript ali program Perl, "
"ki preoblikuje ta izbor v &latex; kodo za matriko. Ne glede na vaše zamisli, "
"jih lahko realizirate z naslednjim vnosom v uporabniškem meniju."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Parameter example 2</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Primer parametra 2</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Parameter example 2</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Primer parametra 2</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: usermenu.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Menu Definition Files</title>"
msgstr "<title>Datoteke z definicijami menija</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can install different menus at runtime for different tasks. When you "
"call the user menu wizard, the current menu definition file is loaded. If "
"you modify it and close the dialog with <guibutton>OK</guibutton>, your "
"changes will be saved and installed as the new user menu. Closing the dialog "
"with <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> will discard all changes."
msgstr ""
"Med izvajanjem lahko namestite različne menije za različna opravila. Ko "
"pokličete čarovnika za uporabniški meni, se naloži trenutna datoteka z "
"definicijo menija. Če ga spremenite in zaprete pogovorno okno z gumbom "
"<guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, bodo vaše spremembe shranjene in nameščene "
"kot nov uporabniški meni. Zapiranje pogovornega okna z <guibutton>Prekliči</"
"guibutton>bo zavrglo vse spremembe."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Menu Definition Files</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Datoteke z definicijami menija</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Menu Definition Files</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Datoteke z definicijami menija</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You are also free to save the modified file in the user menu directory or to "
"load another menu definition file and install it. All user menu definition "
"files must be saved in the local user menu directory of &kile;: "
"<filename>KILE_APP_DIR/usermenu/</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Prav tako lahko spremenjeno datoteko shranite v imenik uporabniškega menija "
"ali naložite drugo datoteko z definicijo menija in jo namestite. Definicije "
"vseh uporabniških menijev datotek mora biti shranjena v imeniku lokalnega "
"uporabniškega menija &kile;: <filename>KILE_APP_DIR/usermenu/</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Look at the example menu definition file <userinput>example.xml</userinput> "
"to see more menu entries with their parameters."
msgstr ""
"Oglejte si datoteko z definicijo menija <userinput>example.xml</userinput>, "
"da vidite več vnosov menija z njihovimi parametri."
